# Build context trimming for the root-context keeper image (Dockerfile.keeper).
# The backend/ and frontend/ services build from their own roots and have their
# own .dockerignore files, so this only affects the keeper/liquidation image.
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
artifacts
cache
typechain
typechain-types
coverage
**/coverage
.openzeppelin
frontend
docs-site
docs
landing
sdk
test
.vscode
*.log
*.tsbuildinfo
